Package entities

Class Appointment

Object
Appointment
public class Appointment extends Object
Represents an appointment in the hospital management system. An appointment is associated with a doctor and a patient, and it tracks the status, date, time, type, prescribed medications, and consultation notes.

      public Appointment(String appointmentID, String patientId, String doctorId, String appointmentDate, String appointmentTime, String appointmentType)
      Constructs an appointment with initial availability, primarily set by a doctor.
      Parameters:
      appointmentID - Unique identifier for the appointment.
      patientId - Patient's ID (may be set later).
      doctorId - Doctor's ID.
      appointmentDate - Date of the appointment.
      appointmentTime - Time of the appointment.
      appointmentType - Type of the appointment.
